      "description": "Set within the Dock East development is this bright and spacious two bedroom, one bathroom apartment.\n\nThe property offers a well-proportioned open-plan living and dining area filled with natural light, leading out to a private balcony — ideal for relaxing or entertaining. The accommodation further comprises two generously sized bedrooms and a contemporary family bathroom, making it perfectly suited to professional sharers, couples, or a small family.\n\n\n\nResidents of Dock East benefit from a range of convenient amenities, including daytime concierge service, a stylish and welcoming lobby with secure mailboxes and parcel storage, as well as secure bicycle storage. The development is modern, well-managed and positioned in a peaceful waterfront setting.\n\nIdeally located just a four minute walk from Crossharbour DLR station, the apartment offers quick and easy access to Canary Wharf, with seamless connections to the Jubilee Line and Elizabeth Line, ensuring effortless commuting into the City and beyond.\n\nCombining excellent transport links, dockside surroundings and modern living, this property presents an exceptional rental opportunity in E14.",
