      "description": "Greystar is delighted to introduce our premium collection of 1, 2 and 3 bedroom apartments at Sailmakers. Located close to Canary Wharf and South Quay Station with a 24Hour Reception and dedicated team based onsite.\n\nThese premium apartments offer spacious, beautifully presented premium living spaces with private balconies overlooking the Canary Wharf area equipped with all your home essentials to the highest specification. Living rooms are equipped with bespoke furniture and a multimedia stand to fit your TV. Kitchens are fully fitted with integrated Smeg appliances. Bathrooms are finished to the highest standards with bathtub and underfloor heating. Bedrooms come carpeted with ottoman king size beds and Hypos mattress and built in wardrobes.\nSailmakers is ideally located just 5 minutes from Canary Wharf providing access to London's underground service via the Jubilee Line and Elizabeth Line. South Quay station is the closest station providing the Docklands Light Railway (DLR) services on your doorstep.\n\nAt Sailmakers, our residents can enjoy an excellent range of services and onsite amenities including:\n\n*\tPet Friendly Apartments\n*\tDedicated Property Manager and Maintenance Team onsite\n*\t24 Hour Reception\n*\tCinema and Lounge on the 8th Floor\n*\tResident Gym on 34th Floor with stunning 360 degrees views of the city\n*\tYoga Room/ Spinning Room/Therapy Room/Circuit Studio/Chillout Room\n*\t35th floor Club Rooms with Pool Table and Library\n*       Private Dining Room to book for your own entertainment\n*\tOutdoor Roof Terraces\n*\tCo-working Spaces and Meeting Rooms onsite\n*\tDry cleaning Services\n*\tPost/Parcel Room\n*      Resident Events\n*\tBike Storage & Secure and Gated Car Park Stacker system\n*      Minimum 12 months Tenancies available\n\n*Images and floorplans used are for illustrative purposes only. Individual apartment sizes, features, furniture and layouts may vary.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\nEnjoy 30 Days of Worry-Free Living with Our Peace of Mind Guarantee!\nAt Greystar, we care so much about the comfort and experience of our residents in their new home, and we are committed to providing you with the best rental experience in the market. If for any reason you feel we haven't met this promise, you can terminate your tenancy by providing 30 days' notice at any time within the first 30 days of your agreement. Terms & Conditions apply*.\n\nVirtual Tours Available - Contact us now to arrange a viewing\n\nFind out more at sailmakers-london.co.uk",
